    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Long flat pieces of wood with slightly curved heads at one end used as a striking implement in various hockey sports.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
